main event: A witness saw an object fall to the ground, which appeared to be a bright green meteor-like object that lit up the sky.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be about 1 mile away from the witness.
The witness called the highway patrol to report the sighting.
A subsequent call indicated the object was possibly seen from miles away.
No photographs were taken of the sighting.
sighted object: a bright green object that fell to the ground
